{"type":"message","id":"c0884236","parentId":"7c8d965f","timestamp":"2026-03-13T07:21:47.640Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gateway is running. But there's a duplicate feishu plugin warning. Let me check if the new web-developer agent is properly configured. Let me also check if the feishu bot can be started properly with the new app credentials.","thinkingSignature":"b72c8887a8abace576a12339eadf3635736a1da770eb0db979d9689bb95567a6"},{"type":"text","text":"Gateway 已运行中 ✅\n\n但是有个问题需要你操作：\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ 需要你在飞书开放平台操作\n\n新部署的 **网站开发工程师** Bot (`cli_a92d03f1b9391bd7`) 需要在飞书开放平台完成以下设置：\n\n1. **创建应用版本并发布**\n2. **添加权限**：\n   - `im:message:send_as_bot` - 发送消息\n   - `im:message:receive` - 接收消息  \n   - `im:chat:member.bot_add` - 添加到群聊\n   - 其他必要权限\n\n3. **创建应用版本**并发布到企业\n\n---\n\n**请问**：你在飞书开放平台上的应用是否已经创建并发布版本了？如果还没有，需要先去飞书开放平台 (https://open.feishu.cn/) 完成应用配置。\n\n完成后告诉我，我们继续进行下一步验证。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":26283,"output":239,"cacheRead":16930,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43452,"cost":{"input":0.0078849,"output":0.0002868,"cacheRead":0.0005078999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0086796}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773386500801}}
